-- Saudi King Calls for Islamic Solidarity Meeting, SPA Reports
-- B y   G l e n   C a r e y
-- 2012-07-22T08:49:47Z
-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2012-07-22/saudi-king-calls-for-islamic-solidarity-meeting-spa-reports.html
Saudi Arabia ’s King Abdullah has
called for an extraordinary Islamic solidarity meeting to be
held in Mecca, the official Saudi Press Agency said, citing a
statement by Foreign Minister Prince Saud al-Faisal.  The meeting at the end of Ramadan will promote unity at
this “delicate time” of the “possibilities of fragmentation
and discord” in the Muslim world, the  news service  reported
Prince Saud as saying.  To contact the reporter on this story:
Glen Carey in Riyadh at 
 gcarey8@bloomberg.net   To contact the editor responsible for this story:
